description: Get detailed data for an environment template.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the environment template that you want to get the detailed data for.

nested_items.name: environmentTemplate
nested_items.description: The detailed data of the requested environment template.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the environment template.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the environment template was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A description of the environment template.

nested_items.name: displayName
nested_items.description: The name of the environment template as displayed in the developer interface.

nested_items.name: encryptionKey
nested_items.description: The customer provided encryption key for the environment template.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the environment template was last modified.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the environment template.

nested_items.name: provisioning
nested_items.description: When included, indicates that the environment template is for customer provisioned and managed infrastructure.

nested_items.name: recommendedVersion
nested_items.description: The ID of the recommended version of the environment template.
